    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1913-05-02T04:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1913-05-02T04:00:00-05:00" n="100"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d100">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 893.00/1641.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">American Chargé d’Affaires</gloss> to
                        the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Peking</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1913-05-02T17:00:00+08:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 2, 1913—5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The President’s message of recognition<note n="1" xml:id="d100fn1">See telegram
                        of April 6, ante.</note> was delivered today to President Yuan. The Minister
                    for Foreign Aifairs has already telegraphed to Washington President Yuan’s
                    expression of gratification.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Williams</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
